{"tid":1978692,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[舔共] 陳奕迅列作中國歌手 現身Gaga慈善騷唱廣東歌","createTime":"2020-04-19T01:34:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-19T11:42:40.000Z","uid":8410,"like":4,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"18767d52dc22878330e65024c9197d223414e840","tid":1978692,"uid":8410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200419/large/1587239090_23ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200419%2Flarge%2F1587239090_23ab.jpg&h=580e4493&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由美國天后Lady GaGa與世界衛生組織（WHO）、Global Citizen合作的8小時馬拉松慈善騷《One World: Together At Home》現時已直播接近兩小時，而香港代表陳奕迅（Eason）於凌晨3時25分出現。Eason在鏡頭出現時，畫面右上角介紹他來自China，而非香港。<br />\n穿上粉藍T裇和戴上米色帽的Eason，首先用廣東話說「Hello，我都想藉着今次機會多謝醫護人員，無私和愛心。」然後分別用普通話和英文再次感謝醫護人員的無私奉獻。<br />\n拿着結他自彈自唱的Eason，唱出20年前的舊廣東歌作品《我甚麼都沒有》。亞洲藝人中，朗朗和Eason已先後出現，至於學友將會稍遲現身。<br />\n<br />\nEason這首舊歌《我甚麼都沒有》是由陳偉作曲、林夕填詞。歌詞中多次提到人生中既已甚麼都沒有，應該灰心至極，不斷沉淪。不過林夕告訴我們並非必然。正如坊間講法「灰到盡頭便會見到曙光」，相信Eason揀唱這首歌，是鼓勵人們在疫境中不要灰心氣餒。Eason在早上約6時30分再度出場，他坐在鋼琴前並以英語介紹自己，並表示由於是第一次在鏡頭前自彈自唱，所以有少許緊張，不過Eason笑言會努力彈好首歌，之後他唱出約翰連儂（John Lennon）的名曲《Love》。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200419/DTJA46LLCZXCHUN2KTJFRWF6QE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200419%2FDTJA46LLCZXCHUN2KTJFRWF6QE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDudFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=1daf2399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20200419%2FDTJA46LLCZXCHUN2KTJFRWF6QE%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_appledailyent%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post&h=a9c5c3c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20200419/DTJA46LLCZXCHUN2KTJFRWF6QE/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_appledailyent&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post</a>"},{"pid":"314043b3a54852ccc99380910ad2b66702f198b1","tid":1978692,"uid":179292,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:49:17.000Z","msg":"大陸e 神，不了"},{"pid":"36fbec3ecb7c2eadf22f4ae8f94bc0aa786f94ef","tid":1978692,"uid":20222,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:51:52.000Z","msg":"係呀<br />\n奶共奶到連香港個名都冇埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d5ac23d3c4e82c81877a01c9fb7e645ab81931","tid":1978692,"uid":30528,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"仲要揀首林夕歌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"953319372f670135bcf26ea4288ed467cf367076","tid":1978692,"uid":187664,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:54:33.000Z","msg":"原片無China 佢自己講代表支那？"},{"pid":"2c523a986603c4641faca10df527756620a4dfec","tid":1978692,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T01:59:06.000Z","msg":"佢都食兩家茶飯好耐喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">英國查黑警違反人權 最後2日deadline</span></span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1978200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1978200</a><br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"7b4d8263e55198f594961868ef981081948c9a5e","tid":1978692,"uid":65638,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T02: